	<p><strong>A colorful, fun, simple and addictive puzzle game for Windows Phone 7.</strong></p>
	
	<p>The objective of the game is to flood all the tiles on the board in the same color. 
	You start in the top left corner and flood the tiles by selecting one of the six colors. 
	When selecting a color you change the color of the top left tile and any adjacent tile with the same color. 
	This way you can flood all the tiles on the grid.</p>
	
	<p>You can also choose between 3 board sizes, 2 game modes, and 30 colorful themes. 
	In the time trial game mode you can also compare your high scores against 
	other players in the online leaderboards.</p>

